Ogden Crane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ogden_Crane 0 Harry Ogden Crane (September 1, 1873 – May 14, 1940) was an American silent film actor. The son of concert singer Sarah Mundell Crane, he was married to Grace Benham. Harry_Ogden_Crane ( September_1 , 1873 – May_14_,_1940 ) was an_American_silent_film_actor .
